It's very slow that search on hive on spark, when hive build a spark session. so I try spark on hive
(1)download spark wget https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/apache/spark/spark-2.3.0/spark-2.3.0-bin-hadoop2.7.tgz;
(2)tar xzf spark-2.3.0-bin-hadoop2.7.tgz;
(3)touch hive-site.xml in directory conf
(4)vi hive-site.xml
